{
  "stem": "1917.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 492.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "That night, the Soviet soldiers came, brought candy, and brought vodka, and started dancing the [NON-ENGLISH] in the middle of that stupid barrack.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "We stayed in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the following day, they took us out, put on us striped uniforms, and marched us between the barbed wire, and took pictures of us-- movie cameras.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thought, gosh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now that's interesting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess we are movie stars, and what?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't understand why they were so interested.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All I really wanted to do is go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I am glad today that they did take those pictures.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were taken from there to Katowice, to a monastery, where we were supposed to-- the rumor was, or maybe they told us-- that we would wait there until the war ended, and then we would be taken to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, I wanted to go to Palestine eventually, but I wanted to go home first.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first night there, I remember very clearly, because we were given nice, small rooms with two beds, and a white sheet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have never, ever seen anything so white.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was gleaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I kept looking at that sheet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I couldn't sleep on it, because I felt dirty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was still filled with lice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still had the-- the-- the-- the clothes that I had in camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- just going to-- I was going to get these sheets dirty, so I had to remove the sheet, and just sleep on the mattress.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they gave us toys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember dolls.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I felt very, very insulted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I realized that they have no idea that the child who survives life and death cannot play with dolls.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
